  "slug": "whatever-floats-your-boat-brownies",
  "title": "\"Whatever Floats Your Boat\" Brownies!",
  "subtitle": "Make it before bed, eat it before work.",
  "excerpt": "\"Whatever Floats Your Boat\" Brownies!. A baking recipe from Rebecca's collection, straightforward, reliable, worth weighing rather than scooping.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "From Rebecca's personal cookbook, a recipe she's made many times in her own kitchen.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "\"Whatever Floats Your Boat\" Brownies!. An American family-table recipe, generous, comforting, built for a crowd. Adjustable for what you need.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Cookies bake fast and reward a chilled dough. Pull them out when the edges set and the middles still look slightly underdone.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
